  "detailed_description": "The old gods have forgotten this land. No one could save our people when darkness started spreading and collecting human souls for its army. <br>Odallus is a classic exploration/action game, inspired by Ghosts’n Goblins, Demon’s Crest and Castlevania. Player takes place of Haggis, a warrior tired of fight who must wield his sword once more to rescue his son from Darkness.<br><br>Original Sound Track: <br><br>Features<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Eight levels open to exploration<br></li><li>Huge bosses<br></li><li>Sharp controls<br></li><li>Rad 8-bit graphics<br></li><li>Thrilling atmosphere<br></li><li>8+ hours of gameplay<br></li><li>50+ types of enemies<br></li><li>Veteran Mode</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "The old gods have forgotten this land. No one could save our people when darkness started spreading and collecting human souls for its army. <br>Odallus is a classic exploration/action game, inspired by Ghosts’n Goblins, Demon’s Crest and Castlevania. Player takes place of Haggis, a warrior tired of fight who must wield his sword once more to rescue his son from Darkness.<br><br>Original Sound Track: <br><br>Features<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Eight levels open to exploration<br></li><li>Huge bosses<br></li><li>Sharp controls<br></li><li>Rad 8-bit graphics<br></li><li>Thrilling atmosphere<br></li><li>8+ hours of gameplay<br></li><li>50+ types of enemies<br></li><li>Veteran Mode</li></ul>",
